      <title>中国最早将于 9 月下调 5 万亿美元抵押贷款利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/china-to-cut-rates-on-5-trillion-mortgages-as-soon-as-september</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国最早将于本月下调超过 5 万亿美元未偿还抵押贷款的利率，以加快降低数百万家庭的借贷成本，刺激消费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/china-to-cut-rates-on-5-trillion-mortgages-as-soon-as-september</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 08:05:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
